src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68632a5090a9e35624ffe6451ca7e7ef341867e2","tid":257683,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢係串得起，大家唔好再盲反</blockquote><br />\n事實證明佢係串唔起</blockquote><br />\n一個串唔起既人做到世界第一，你係咪串緊全部人類都係垃圾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/121949_fa47f5727f91eeab1c06bab4b544b665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F121949_fa47f5727f91eeab1c06bab4b544b665.jpg&h=57a0369b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你地駁埋先：係咪世界第一就要串？/串得起就要串？</blockquote><br />\n如果你要咁睇的確全人類都係垃圾<br />\n同埋唔好意思佢只係<span style=\"color: red;\">全人類既世界第一姐</span><br />\n先不論國際，世界第一定要串亦唔等於串得起就一定要串<br />\n依家佢的確係串左，咁事實又證明左佢串唔起alpha go，所以比人binc有咩好駁，我唔明有咩好維護同有咩好駁</blockquote><br />\n你up乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢串係唔可取，但點解串得起唔可以串？<br />\n你估連登仔唔知柯潔圍棋勁咩？佢地笑鳩緊佢既國籍咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而柯潔的確係輸左亦都冇得維護，但佢賽後甚至賽前都已經好謙虛講左唔會夠alphago黎，我唔明點解連登仔係都要捉住成年前講過既野無限放大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e07d68f6dca0f834e619bfb5a30d85151cda2e","tid":257683,"uid":50020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢係串得起，大家唔好再盲反</blockquote><br />\n事實證明佢係串唔起</blockquote><br />\n一個串唔起既人做到世界第一，你係咪串緊全部人類都係垃圾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/121949_fa47f5727f91eeab1c06bab4b544b665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F121949_fa47f5727f91eeab1c06bab4b544b665.jpg&h=57a0369b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你地駁埋先：係咪世界第一就要串？/串得起就要串？</blockquote><br />\n如果你要咁睇的確全人類都係垃圾<br />\n同埋唔好意思佢只係<span style=\"color: red;\">全人類既世界第一姐</span><br />\n先不論國際，世界第一定要串亦唔等於串得起就一定要串<br />\n依家佢的確係串左，咁事實又證明左佢串唔起alpha go，所以比人binc有咩好駁，我唔明有咩好維護同有咩好駁</blockquote><br />\n你up乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢串係唔可取，但點解串得起唔可以串？<br />\n你估連登仔唔知柯潔圍棋勁咩？佢地笑鳩緊佢既國籍咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而柯潔的確係輸左亦都冇得維護，但佢賽後甚至賽前都已經好謙虛講左唔會夠alphago黎，我唔明點解連登仔係都要捉住成年前講過既野無限放大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又uo乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然唔可取咪唔應該做囉，咁佢係咪做左先<br />\n柯潔唔輸理得佢菲律賓藉都唔洗比人串啦<br />\n作為一個世界第一，講左出去既說話收得返架？<br />\n你估真係連登仔咁一句呢局唔算咁就算呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c72e7b6165e03153993a2602b84f5216c830cb","tid":257683,"uid":11753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"點解串得起就唔可以串都噏得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最基本做人態度都冇重好意思聲大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔會好似班傻鳩中坑以為有得叼光所以起勢奶袋底呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"2ecf237c39bd163486654f4a8e01793715d98c54","tid":257683,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當一個人嘅技術已經去到世界頂尖，<br />\n佢所代表嘅就係人類水平，<br />\n國籍已經唔重要。</blockquote><br />\n但人品係作為人嘅基礎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果連